 Nollywood actor Ali Nuhu was on Wednesday, March 16, unveiled as the latest Checkers Custard ambassador at the Presidential Suite Hall, Tahir Guest Palace, Kano. Fondly called ‘Sarki Ali’, his partnership with the custard brand will see him in the next few months “bring to the good people of Kano and Nigeria, special packages and opportunities in order to fulfil our respective roles in society,” said the Managing Director of Checkers Africa Limited, Karan Checker. He further stressed that the interest and choice of Nuhu was due to his amiable character, top-notch talent and humility. Nuhu also expressed delight in joining the Checkers family. Checkers Custard is produced by Checkers Africa Limited and comes in three exciting flavours of Vanilla, Banana and Milk 3-in-1.